<!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="pt-br">
        <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8">
            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/resultstyle.css">
            <title>RESULTADO ELEIÇÃO - 2024</title>
        </head>
        <body>
            <header>
                <div class="cabecalho">
                    <div class="logo">
                        <img src="/imgs/Logo2(FundoTransparente-Cabecalho-Logo-Escrita).webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="headerSocial">
                        <ul class="headerSocial-links">
                            <a class="gitHub" href="https://github.com/LucasLiSan/eleicaoPingodeGente"><li>github</li></a>
                            <a class="instagram" href="https://www.instagram.com/lukastopo/"><li>instagram</li></a>
                            <a class="whatsapp" href=""><li>whatsapp</li></a>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <nav>
                    <input type="radio" name="optAnalysis" id="general" value="geral">
                    <label for="general">GERAL</label>
                    <input type="radio" name="optAnalysis" id="analysis" value="analise">
                    <label for="analysis">ANALISE POR SALA</label>
                </nav>
            </header>
            <main>
                <section class="general">
                    <h1>CANDIDATO</h1>
                    <div class="apuracao">
                        <span><span class="percent">30%</span> URNAS APURADAS</span>
                        <progress value="30" max="100"></progress>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absentee-votes">
                        <div class="votesTotal">
                            <span class="votesPercent">80%</span>
                            <label for="votesPercent">VOTANTES</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absentee">
                            <span class="absenteePercent">20%</span>
                            <label for="absenteePercent">AUSENTES</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="candidates">
                        <div class="moreVotes">
                            <% candidates.slice(0, 2).forEach((candidate, index) => { %>
                                <div id="<%= index === 0 ? 'first' : 'second' %>">
                                    <figure class="<%= index === 0 ? 'img-first' : 'img-second' %>">
                                        <img src="<%= candidate.candidatePic %>" alt="Candidato-<%= index + 1 %>">
                                        <figcaption><%= index + 1 %>º LUGAR</figcaption>
                                    </figure>
                                    <div class="name-party">
                                        <input type="text" name="Candidato" id="candidato-<%= index === 0 ? 'First' : 'Second' %>" value="<%= candidate.name %>" disabled>
                                        <input type="text" name="Party" id="party-<%= index === 0 ? 'First' : 'Second' %>" value="<%= candidate.party %>" disabled>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="votesCandidate">
                                        <% 
                                            const percentage = totalVotes > 0 ? ((candidate.votes / totalVotes) * 100).toFixed(2) : 0;
                                        %>
                                        <span class="percentVotes"><%= percentage %>%</span>
                                        <input type="number" name="votes" id="qtdVotes<%= index + 1 %>" value="<%= candidate.votes %>" disabled>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            <% }); %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="lessVotes">
                            <% candidates.slice(2, 5).forEach((candidate, index) => { %>
                                <div id="<%= ['third', 'fourth', 'fifth'][index] %>">
                                    <figure class="img-<%= ['third', 'fourth', 'fifth'][index] %>">
                                        <img src="<%= candidate.candidatePic %>" alt="Candidato-<%= index + 3 %>">
                                        <figcaption><%= index + 3 %>º LUGAR</figcaption>
                                    </figure>
                                    <div class="name-party">
                                        <input type="text" name="Candidato" id="candidato-<%= ['Third', 'Fourth', 'Fifth'][index] %>" value="<%= candidate.name %>" disabled>
                                        <input type="text" name="Party" id="party-<%= ['Third', 'Fourth', 'Fifth'][index] %>" value="<%= candidate.party %>" disabled>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="votesCandidate">
                                        <% 
                                            const percentage = totalVotes > 0 ? ((candidate.votes / totalVotes) * 100).toFixed(2) : 0;
                                        %>
                                        <span class="percentVotes"><%= percentage %>%</span>
                                        <input type="number" name="votes" id="qtdVotes<%= index + 3 %>" value="<%= candidate.votes %>" disabled>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            <% }); %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="voteAnalysis">
                        <div class="blank">
                            <span class="percentVotes">50%</span>
                            <input type="number" name="votes" id="qtdVotesBlank" value="11" disabled>
                            <label for="qtdVotesNull">VOTOS EM BRANCO</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="nulls">
                            <span class="percentVotes">40%</span>
                            <input type="number" name="votes" id="qtdVotesNull" value="7" disabled>
                            <label for="qtdVotesNull">VOTOS NULOS</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="valids">
                            <span class="percentVotes">30%</span>
                            <input type="number" name="votes" id="qtdVotesValids" value="1111" disabled>
                            <label for="qtdVotesNull">VOTOS VÁLIDOS</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="analysis"></section>
            </main>
            <footer>
                <div class="infos">
                    <p class="project">Para simular uma eleição real para o "Projeto eleição" na EMEB Pingo de Gente, foi elaborada uma urna eletrônica seguindo os padrões do urna eletrônica brasileira e, para os resultados, uma pagina de apuração de votos.</p>
                    <div class="urnaAviso">
                        <h3><a href="https://www.justicaeleitoral.jus.br/urna-eletronica/"> URNA ELETRÔNICA DO BRASIL</a></h3>
                        <p>O sistema de votação eletrônico brasileiro permite o exercício da cidadania com maior segurança. A urna foi desenvolvida para computar votos de forma segura e sigilosa, atendendo à demanda e às características específicas do Brasil.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footerSocial">
                    <ul class="footerSocial-links">
                        <a class="gitHub" href="https://github.com/LucasLiSan/eleicaoPingodeGente"><li>github</li></a>
                        <a class="instagram" href="https://www.instagram.com/lukastopo/"><li>instagram</li></a>
                        <a class="whatsapp" href=""><li>whatsapp</li></a>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </body>
    </html>